Watches are the perfect way to complement the clothes you wear. Are you looking for a simple and elegant watch that can stand up to the demands of daily use yet be stylish enough to wear on those classy evenings out? Perhaps you think of a watch as an accessory and aim to add a few more to that collection of yours. Whatever the need may be the Maxima analog watch for women seems to be the appropriate choice. This casual watch from Maxima sports a classy analog dial driven by a battery powered quartz mechanism that keeps both you and the watch ticking right through the day. 

Body and Design

The analog watch from Maxima comes with a leather strap. The leather strap makes this watch very comfortable to wear over long periods of time. The watch also features a rectangular dial that is encased in a steel bezel. The simplistic design of the rectangular dial with its three display hands really accentuates the beauty of such a watch.

Functions and Other Features

The women's analog watch from Maxima is designed to be water resistant as well as water resistant to a depth of 30 m making your next trip to one of those scenic waterfalls even more enjoyable.

Watches are the perfect way to complement the clothes you wear. Are you looking for a simple and elegant watch that can stand up to the demands of daily use yet be stylish enough to wear on those classy evenings out? Perhaps you think of a watch as an accessory and aim to add a few more to that collection of yours. Whatever the need may be the Maxima analog watch for women seems to be the appropriate choice. This casual watch from Maxima sports a classy analog dial driven by a battery powered quartz mechanism that keeps both you and the watch ticking right through the day. 

Body and Design

The analog watch from Maxima comes with a leather strap. The leather strap makes this watch very comfortable to wear over long periods of time. The watch also features a rectangular dial that is encased in a steel bezel. The simplistic design of the rectangular dial with its three display hands really accentuates the beauty of such a watch.

Functions and Other Features

The women's analog watch from Maxima is designed to be water resistant as well as water resistant to a depth of 30 m making your next trip to one of those scenic waterfalls even more enjoyable.
